window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>“Greetings from the Kel Confederacy of Systems.”</p> <p>Those simple words turned Kayden Reynolds’ view of the galaxy upside down. Humanity assumed that the aliens whose mastery of genetic engineering helped power our ascent to the stars were long dead.</p> <p>They were wrong.</p> <p>When Kayden and his crew of beautiful women meet them, they’re quickly embroiled in the conflict between the Kel and their ancient rivals, whose knowledge of technological engineering is unrivaled.</p> <p>As the only being in the galaxy to successfully combine genetic engineering and cybernetics, Kayden takes on the seemingly impossible task of ending the eons-long war.</p> <p>…Ideally before their war engulfs humanity.</p>"; 
